text: Admetula superstes is a species of sea snail, a marine gastropod mollusk in the family Cancellariidae, the nutmeg snails. ==Description== ==Distribution== This species is found along New Zealand. ==References== * Bouchet P. & Petit R.E. (2008). New species and new records of southwest Pacific Cancellariidae. The Nautilus 122(1): 1–18. ==External links== * Category:Cancellariidae Category:Gastropods described in 1930
title: Admetula superstes
